channel.description:
Where everything cool is HOTT!  

The latest in celebrity gossip and entertainment news from DatzHott.com

"DatzHott" is a digital content distributor that provide audiences with information about the latest things happening in urban pop culture.

Over the past six years, we've interviewed Hollywood's biggest celebrities, shot numerous films and music videos; along with various web series. As our goal, is to ultimately, give audiences the opportunity to visit a one stop shop for anything dealing with pop culture. 

"DatzHott" is much more than a statement that defines pop culture. It's the actual voice that set the trends as we are best summed up through the slogan: "Where Everything Cool is Hott!"

Our website DatzHott.com currently receives 2 Million monthly page views per month.

We are always open for celebrity interviews, red carpet events, music videos, and collaborations. 

Feel free to use the information below to reach out. Serious queries only.
